na Kaif as Harley Quinn  More than just innerwear, Jockey Woman's new collection is an invitation to self-care, love, and quiet celebration  Kareena Kapoor Khan just roared in a Sabyasachi Leopard print saree and we are obsessed  Red outfit Inspiration for Karva Chauth 2025: Alia Bhatt to Aishwarya Rai Bachchan  6 celeb-inspired couple fashion for Diwali party 2025: Ranbir Kapoor-Alia Bhatt to Vicky Kaushal-Katrina Kaif  Sonam Kapoor serves boho maternity vibes, but her elephant bag steals the show  Meet celebrity hairstylist who charges Rs 20,000- Rs 50,000 per haircut; Kajal Aggarwal, Dino Morea and others swear by him  Suhana Khan oozes glam in Rs 2,95,000 gown while Ananya Panday dazzles in Rs 78,000 rhinestone dress at Ba***ds of Bollywood premiere  Alia Bhatt looks HOT in Tom Ford's iconic Gucci dress from 1996 without overdoing it, styled by Rhea Kapoor  Indian wrestler Aman Sehrawat won a bronze medal at the Paris Olympics in 2024 in the men's 57-kg freestyle. Only recently, he took to his Instagram handle and shared a few candid pictures with Dilip Joshi, also known as Jethalal from Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah. The actor celebrated Aman's victory by gifting him a snack hamper and the iconic jalebi fafda. Dilip also shared the post on his story, expressing delight.  Dropping the pictures, the Olympics bronze medalist wrote, \\\"\\u0906\\u091c \\u092e\\u0941\\u091d\\u0947 \\u091c\\u0947\\u0920\\u093e\\u0932\\u093e\\u0932 (\\u0926\\u093f\\u0932\\u0940\\u092a \\u091c\\u094b\\u0936\\u0940\\u091c\\u0940) @maakasamdilipjoshi \\u0915\\u094b \\u092e\\u093f\\u0932\\u0915\\u0930 \\u092c\\u0939\\u0941\\u0924 \\u0905\\u091a\\u094d\\u091b\\u093e \\u0932\\u0917\\u093e\\u0964 \\u0907\\u0928\\u0915\\u094b \\u0926\\u0947\\u0916\\u0915\\u0930 \\\"\\u0924\\u093e\\u0930\\u0915 \\u092e\\u0947\\u0939\\u0924\\u093e \\u0915\\u093e \\u0909\\u0932\\u094d\\u091f\\u093e \\u091a\\u0936\\u094d\\u092e\\u093e\\\" \\u092e\\u0947\\u0902 \\u092e\\u0941\\u091d\\u0947 \\u0939\\u092e\\u0947\\u0936\\u093e \\u0939\\u0902\\u0938\\u0940 \\u0914\\u0930 \\u0916\\u0941\\u0936\\u0940 \\u092e\\u093f\\u0932\\u0924\\u0940 \\u0925\\u0940, \\u092c\\u0939\\u0941\\u0924-\\u092c\\u0939\\u0941\\u0924 \\u0927\\u0928\\u094d\\u092f\\u0935\\u093e\\u0926 \\u092e\\u0941\\u091d\\u0938\\u0947 \\u092e\\u093f\\u0932\\u0928\\u0947 \\u0915\\u0947 \\u0932\\u093f\\u090f\\u0964 (Today I felt great meeting Jethalal (Dilip Joshi). Watching him in Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah Makes me happy. Thank you so much for paying a visit to me).\\\"  Take a look at the post here:      On the other hand, dropping the pictures from his meeting with Aman Sehrawat,Dilip Joshiwrote, \\\"Celebrating @amansehrawat057's Bronze Medal win the best way I know- the Jalebi-Fafda way! Honoured to have met and spent time with @amansehrawat057. What an inspiration!\\\"  Take a look at Dilip's Instagram story here:    Well, after his win at the Paris Olympics 2024, Aman expressed his fondness forTMKOC. While interacting with the media, the wrestler was asked about what he enjoys doing in his free time apart from practicing wrestling. To this, he stated, \\\"I like to watch Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah during my free time.\\\"  The video went viral on social media platforms as netizens resonated with Aman's emotions. Dilip Joshi re-shared the video on his Instagram handle and thanked him for his good remarks. Extending best wishes for the bronze medal win, theHum Aapke Hain Kounactor commented, \\\"Thank you, Aman Sehrawat; we will continue to entertain you! Congratulations to you and all of our Olympians for making our country proud.\\\"  For those who are unfamiliar, Dilip Joshi has been a part of the show since its inception. His role as Jethalal has given numerous iconic onscreen moments to the audience. TMKOC is among the longest-running shows, and recently completed 4000 episodes.  ALSO READ:In PICS: Hina Khan calls herself 'PLUVIOPHILE; enjoys Mumbai 'baarish' with serene view\"}"